description:
In this week’s mini-episode, Kate and Doree discover the shocking truth about YM’s Say Anything column, thanks to some listeners on the inside! Then they discuss how to bring your favorite products along while traveling, recommend some long-lasting eye liner, and get a tip from a listener on dealing with fitted bed sheets.

To leave a voicemail for a future mini-ep, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.

This episode is sponsored by:

  • Health Warrior Chia Bars - Go to Healthwarrior.com/forever and enter promo code Forever35 at checkout for 25% off your first order.


Theme music by Riot.
